For all those that have asked and to correct the responses from a few people, Federal E-file is completely free.  The State e-file is not free.  It is free to download the State forms, but to e-file your state return using TurboTax H&B, it costs 19.95.  So you will be able to fill it out and have it prepared and ready, but when it comes time to submit, you will be charged 19.95 (for the first State return, 39.95 for any additional).  

You can, however, print the State return out and mail it in for free or just take the information from the Turbotax State return and submit it through your State's free e-file service.

This program installed and worked perfectly for me on Windows 7 Ultimate x64.
